<div class="page-container">
  <h1 class="page-title">SHIPPING & RETURNS</h1>
  
  <div class="page-content-wrapper rte">
    <p><strong>SHIPPING & RETURNS POLICY</strong></p>
    <p>THANK YOU FOR SHOPPING WITH TWOTISM. BELOW ARE OUR POLICIES REGARDING SHIPPING, FULFILLMENT, AND RETURNS. BY PLACING AN ORDER, YOU AGREE TO THESE TERMS.</p>

    <h3>SECTION 1 - PRODUCTION & FULFILLMENT</h3>
    <p>TWOTISM PRODUCTS ARE CUSTOM MADE OR PRINTED TO ORDER. PLEASE ALLOW A FULFILLMENT TIMELINE OF <strong>2 TO 3 WEEKS</strong> FOR YOUR APPAREL ITEMS TO BE MANUFACTURED AND PACKAGED BEFORE DEPARTING OUR WAREHOUSE. ORDERS ARE FULFILLED ON A FIRST-COME, FIRST-SERVED BASIS. YOU WILL RECEIVE A TRACKING NOTIFICATION ONCE SHIPPED.</p>

    <h3>SECTION 2 - DOMESTIC & INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING</h3>
    <p><strong>DOMESTIC SHIPPING (UNITED STATES)</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>SHIPPED VIA LEADING CARRIERS SUCH AS DHL, USPS, UPS, AND FEDEX.</li>
      <li>DELIVERY TAKES <strong>3 TO 7 BUSINESS DAYS</strong> AFTER DEPARTING OUR WAREHOUSE.</li>
      <li>SHIPPING COSTS ARE CALCULATED NATIVELY AT CHECKOUT BASED ON WEIGHT AND DESTINATION.</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING (WORLDWIDE)</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>WE SHIP GLOBALLY TO MOST COUNTRIES SUPPORTED BY OUR FULFILLMENT NETWORK.</li>
      <li>DELIVERY GENERALLY REQUIRES <strong>7 TO 21 BUSINESS DAYS</strong> FROM THE SHIPMENT DATE.</li>
      <li><strong>DUTIES, VAT, & CUSTOMS FEES:</strong> INTERNATIONAL SHIPMENTS ARE SENT DDU (DELIVERED DUTY UNPAID). THE RECIPIENT IS RESPONSIBLE FOR ALL IMPORT DUTIES, VAT, TARIFFS, AND CUSTOMS FEES. THESE FEES CANNOT BE CALCULATED IN ADVANCE AND MUST BE PAID PRIOR TO DELIVERY.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>SECTION 3 - SHIPMENT TRACKING</h3>
    <p>TRACKING DATA WILL BE EMAILED TO YOU ONCE THE SHIPPING LABEL IS CREATED. PLEASE ALLOW <strong>24 TO 48 HOURS</strong> FOR THE CARRIER TO SCAN YOUR PACKAGE AND POPULATE UPDATES INTO THEIR SYSTEM.</p>

    <h3>SECTION 4 - LOST, STOLEN, OR DAMAGED PACKAGES</h3>
    <p>TWOTISM IS NOT LIABLE FOR CARRIER DELAYS, LOST OR STOLEN PACKAGES, OR DELIVERIES MADE TO INCORRECT ADDRESSES SUBMITTED BY BUYERS. ONCE IN-TRANSIT SCAN DATA IS GENERATED, OWNERSHIP CONVEYS TO THE BUYER. IF YOUR TRACKING LOG CONFIRMS DELIVERY BUT YOU CANNOT LOCATE IT, CONTACT THE RESPECTIVE CARRIER DIRECTLY.</p>

    <h3>SECTION 5 - ADDRESS CORRECTIONS & UNDELIVERABLE SHIPMENTS</h3>
    <p>ADDRESS CORRECTIONS CANNOT BE GUARANTEED. PLEASE DOUBLE-CHECK YOUR SHIPPING FIELDS BEFORE SUBMITTING AN ORDER. IF A SHIPMENT IS RETURNED TO US AS UNDELIVERABLE DUE TO AN INVALID ADDRESS, YOU ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR EXTRA REDELIVERY CHARGES.</p>

    <h3>SECTION 6 - STRICT NO RETURNS, NO REFUNDS, & NO EXCHANGES</h3>
    <p>DUE TO THE HIGHLY LIMITED RUNS OF TWOTISM CHUD DROPS, <strong>ALL SALES ARE EXTREMELY FINAL</strong>. WE DO NOT ACCEPT RETURNS FOR REFUNDS, SIZING EXCHANGES, OR CANCELLATIONS UNDER ANY CIRCUMSTANCES.</p>

    <h3>SECTION 7 - DAMAGED OR INCORRECT ITEMS</h3>
    <p>IF YOU RECEIVE AN APPAREL ITEM THAT IS DEFECTIVE OR IN THE EVENT OF A FULFILLMENT ERROR (E.G. WRONG DESIGN OR SIZE RECEIVED), PLEASE CONTACT US WITHIN <strong>5 CALENDAR DAYS</strong> OF DELIVERY.</p>
    <p><strong>REPORTING PROTOCOLS:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>CONTACT US VIA THE FOOTER'S CONTACT FORM.</li>
      <li>PROVIDE YOUR ORDER NUMBER.</li>
      <li>ATTACH CLEAR PHOTOS DOCUMENTING THE DEFECT OR INCORRECT ITEM.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>ONCE VERIFIED, WE WILL COVER SHIPPING AND ARRANGE FOR A REPLACEMENT AT NO EXTRA COST.</p>
  </div>
</div>

